1rst Game: Players compete to keep their teams balloon in the air. Each team has a goalie who is responsible for keeping their teams balloon in the air. The first teams balloon to touch the ground looses. The loosing teams goalie is eliminated. The winning teams goalie is awarded 3 points!

2nd Game: Player compete to see who can hold a plank the longest. The first player to fail is eliminated.

3rd Game: Players compete to see who can hold a wall sit the longest. First player to fail is eliminated.

4th Game: Players compete in a push up contest. Player with the least # of push ups is eliminated.

5th Game: Players determine someone to throw an object at random. Players then race to be the first to touch the object. The players then repeat this with the winner of each round sitting out. The final player standing is eliminated.

6th Game: Players compete in a sit up contest. Player with the least # of sit ups is eliminated.

7th Game: Player compete in a game of Karate. The first player defeated is eliminated.

8th Game: Players compete to see who can throw an object the farthest. Shortest distance is eliminated.

9th Game: Players compete in a footrace. The slower player is eliminated!